## Context
The dataset is scraped from gamespot.com 
GameSpot is a video gaming website that provides news, reviews, previews, downloads, and other information on video games. The site was launched on May 1, 1996,

##Content
This dataset includes 14802 game rate and review Jobs with attributes such as 'Games names, Console, Score'
##Acknowledgements
The data in this dataset has been scraped using BeautifulSoup from the gamespot website
